      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-spec 2004 BMW M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear, visceral acceleration. The chassis is well-sorted, featuring reinforced subframe mounting points and a limited-slip differential that ensures optimal torque distribution. Recent mechanical maintenance includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and a cooling system refresh with an aluminum radiator. Equipped with a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and staggered 19-inch forged wheels, this M3 provides the precise tactile feedback and analog engagement that defines the E46 platform. The exterior maintains its structural integrity with minor cosmetic wear consistent with spirited road use.",
